    "description": "《轨界新生》是一款生存建造游戏，你将通过搜刮资源，从零开始逐节拼装专属列车。​采集濒危植物重建生态群落，穿梭于轨道纵横交错的异星世界，发掘外星方尖碑——这一切都在你移动的庇护所中进行。​支持 1-4 人联机协作​。<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/92f8ea48866bd0d23c7ede4b9f751a1c.webp?t=1767726052\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>从零造车</strong>: 从一无所有开始，在荒野中搜寻资源，逐步拼装车厢、建造甲板、搭建轨道车。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/86575f9598fe712ebe38c5f05f04a101.poster.avif?t=1767726052\" width=780 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/86575f9598fe712ebe38c5f05f04a101.webm?t=1767726052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/86575f9598fe712ebe38c5f05f04a101.mp4?t=1767726052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>多人联机</strong>: 可单人游玩，或与好友组队合作。<br><br></li><li><strong>轨道世界</strong>: 穿梭于贯穿山脉与潜入深海的轨道网络。你是选择徒步冒险，还是运筹帷幄，驾驶列车突破地形，抵达终点呢？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/33bdc970342ade923a2ced8528a6d9dc.poster.avif?t=1767726052\" width=780 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/33bdc970342ade923a2ced8528a6d9dc.webm?t=1767726052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/33bdc970342ade923a2ced8528a6d9dc.mp4?t=1767726052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>艰险生存</strong>: 列车外的濒死世界危机四伏——每一步都需对抗窒息、饥饿与星球本身的致命反噬。<br></li><li><strong>精密管理</strong>: 需要你全面掌控火车系统——调配电力网络、规划资源流向、建立净水循环，还可以自定义驾驶控制面板，找到你最喜欢的操作逻辑。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/a134dc2dd773728856a766e503f58d07.poster.avif?t=1767726052\" width=780 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/a134dc2dd773728856a766e503f58d07.webm?t=1767726052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/a134dc2dd773728856a766e503f58d07.mp4?t=1767726052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>生态方舟</strong>: 从濒临灭绝的外星世界抢救珍稀植物，在火车上精心重建生物群落。<br></li><li><strong>解开谜团</strong>: 探索废弃的殖民者前哨站与神秘外星方尖碑，解开重重轨道吞噬星球背后的真相。<br></li><li><strong>拯救行动</strong>: 驾驶火车沿终极轨道冲破天际，执行孤注一掷的拯救任务：拯救自己、拯救星球生态、拯救散落各地的殖民者。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/2d4224d9bc78e439f61a446b453ea63f.poster.avif?t=1767726052\" width=780 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/2d4224d9bc78e439f61a446b453ea63f.webm?t=1767726052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340970/extras/2d4224d9bc78e439f61a446b453ea63f.mp4?t=1767726052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
